e applied to transformer-based architectures (e.g., BERT, RoBERTa) and evaluated across diverse NLP tasks including text classification, intent recognition, and dialogue state tracking. Its potential impact lies in enabling AI systems to adapt fluidly across communication styles—critical for real-world deployment in social media monitoring, mental health chatbots, or cross-cultural customer support—while preserving hard-won knowledge from formal training phases.",
